  cardName: "Thi\u1EC3m \u0110i\u1EC7n"
  cardImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f7488f3d54087e646815d451a1e59b58, type: 3}
  cardDescription: "Giai \u0111o\u1EA1n h\xE0nh \u0111\u1ED9ng, n\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n
    kh\xF4ng c\xF3 [Thi\u1EC3m \u0110i\u1EC7n] trong khu v\u1EF1c ph\xE1n x\xE9t
    c\u1EE7a m\xECnh, b\u1EA1n c\xF3 th\u1EC3 s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng l\xE1 b\xE0i n\xE0y
    l\xEAn b\u1EA3n th\xE2n.\r\nGiai \u0111o\u1EA1n ph\xE1n x\xE9t c\u1EE7a m\u1ED9t
    ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u01A1i, n\u1EBFu h\u1ECD c\xF3 [Thi\u1EC3m \u0110i\u1EC7n]
    trong khu v\u1EF1c ph\xE1n x\xE9t, h\u1ECD ti\u1EBFn h\xE0nh 1 l\u1EA7n ph\xE1n
    x\xE9t, n\u1EBFu k\u1EBFt qu\u1EA3 ph\xE1n x\xE9t tr\xEAn l\xE0:\r\nCh\u1EA5t
    \u2660 v\xE0 \u0111i\u1EC3m s\u1ED1 trong kho\u1EA3ng t\u1EEB 2 \u0111\u1EBFn
    9: h\u1ECD nh\u1EADn 3 \u0111i\u1EC3m s\xE1t th\u01B0\u01A1ng thu\u1ED9c t\xEDnh
    L\xF4i v\xF4 ngu\u1ED3n v\xE0 b\u1ECF \u0111i l\xE1 b\xE0i n\xE0y.\r\nNgo\u1EA1i
    tr\u1EEB c\xE1c tr\u01B0\u1EDDng h\u1EE3p tr\xEAn: di chuy\u1EC3n [Thi\u1EC3m
    \u0110i\u1EC7n] sang khu v\u1EF1c ph\xE1n x\xE9t c\u1EE7a ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u01A1i
    k\u1EBF ti\u1EBFp theo th\u1EE9 t\u1EF1 v\xF2ng ch\u01A1i."
